casebody.data:
Kenneth S. THOMSON, Trustee in Bankruptcy of W. L. Koughan, etc., Appellant, v. L. M. WILLIAMSON, Appellee. No. 6324. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. March 16, 1931.

Before RUDKIN, WILBUR, and SAW-TELLE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to motion of counsel for appellant, ordered appeal dismissed; mandate forthwith.
